    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关于近期部分玩家有留言/质疑游戏有抄袭/换皮《魔域地牢》的嫌疑，【肉鸽独立团】开发商在此正式回应一下，开发商是得到《魔域地牢》官方正版授权全新开发的，对比《魔域地牢》我们升级了装备系统，让战斗策略和构筑方式更丰富，并且重置了美术风格，有更强的故事演绎效果，在战斗地图加入障碍物系统，地图大小变化等等，以及更多的优化调整和内容新增，我们游戏还有特殊挑战玩法以及构筑内容这块，我们选择用的是偏重于构筑策略放弃了快速的爽感，不同流派都能通关，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/edf5a37fc3b018260c37664dfb43f5b6.avif?t=1734084618\" width=600 height=162 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据自己的战斗风格选择战士或魔法师，解锁迥然不同的技能和流派。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏还拥有超过70张职业卡牌，随着游戏进度不断解锁新卡牌，为队友提升战力的新手引导员、擅长远距离攻击和流血伤害的洗剪吹大师等等，你可以自由组建不同的流派和组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/5695713cc1150a86597c08a9cc445819.poster.avif?t=1734084618\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/5695713cc1150a86597c08a9cc445819.webm?t=1734084618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/5695713cc1150a86597c08a9cc445819.mp4?t=1734084618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/cbbda93387bd522056cbf228f8329372.avif?t=1734084618\" width=600 height=162 /></span>游戏中有超过十几个随机事件，风浪越大鱼越贵，你敢不敢放手一搏？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏还提供了数十种魔法牌、道具牌以及武器牌，在战斗结束后商店均会随机出现，搭配你的最强牌组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/78de0df454ccb606a0ec0bebcc26619b.poster.avif?t=1734084618\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/78de0df454ccb606a0ec0bebcc26619b.webm?t=1734084618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/78de0df454ccb606a0ec0bebcc26619b.mp4?t=1734084618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/78fa0ba341a7f37c70ededeb224091ac.avif?t=1734084618\" width=600 height=162 /></span>融合棋盘和战棋玩法，在有限的空间中玩出无限的可能，如何安排每个回合的战术将成为游戏获胜的关键！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/2ce8504dddfb490faab357121b05cc63.poster.avif?t=1734084618\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/2ce8504dddfb490faab357121b05cc63.webm?t=1734084618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/2ce8504dddfb490faab357121b05cc63.mp4?t=1734084618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/e8ce700a42c8b54d792d5ecd52fac9df.avif?t=1734084618\" width=600 height=162 /></span>超过数十个不同特性的怪物和首领，完全不一样的技能和攻击方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >优先攻击首领还是烦人的随从？什么时机哪个位置攻击才最合适？这都是你需要思考的问题！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/8867117ae20dda124a21a4168f2d8c44.poster.avif?t=1734084618\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/8867117ae20dda124a21a4168f2d8c44.webm?t=1734084618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077400/extras/8867117ae20dda124a21a4168f2d8c44.mp4?t=1734084618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如您对游戏有任何意见和建议，欢迎进群讨论！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《代号肉鸽：流放之地》玩家交流群：738398261</p>",
